| Layer | Technology | Version |
|---|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js (App Router) | 15.3.8 |
| Runtime | Node.js | ≥18 |
| Language | TypeScript | ^5 |
| Styling | TailwindCSS  | ^4 |
| CSS Processor | PostCSS | ^4 |
| Font | Inter (Google Fonts) | Variable |
| Icon Library | React-Icons (`react-icons/fi`) | ^5.5.0 |
| UI Framework | React | ^19.0.0 |
| Database | MongoDB Atlas | Native driver ^6.16.0 |
| Image CDN | Cloudinary | SDK ^2.6.1 |
| Payment Processing | Razorpay *(Package present, UPI flow active)* | ^2.9.6 |
| Build Bundler | Turbopack (via `next dev --turbopack`) | Bundled with Next 15 |
| Linter | ESLint | ^9 |

